{"tid":619352,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"啱啱用0.0 1秒揼咗女朋友對黑絲落街","createTime":"2018-04-06T14:27:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-06T15:07:43.000Z","uid":165057,"like":1,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"de984ff313469808cd65f01d5a6d48e1bc50b58f","tid":619352,"uid":165057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T14:27:49.000Z","msg":"女朋友今日着咗黑絲短裙上咗我屋企，入𨋢嗰陣我已經忍唔住手又揸佢波又揸佢屎忽。個衰妹今日着得真係好鬼死誘人，<br />\n<br />\n一入到屋我就忍唔住推咗佢入我間房，係咁嘴佢又揸佢對大波波佢對波真係大到一隻手到站晒，佢high到係咁攞個屎忽磨我， 我忍唔住叫佢瞓喺度落腳板底磨我碌鳩，本身唔係腳膠腳我終於都明白啲巴打或腳膠有幾正。<br />\n<br />\n跟住我除咗佢對黑絲攞上手一索，哇屌你老母好撚臭啊。順手將對黑絲揼咗落街。條女見到即刻笑到卡卡聲，眼淚水都標埋出嚟，碌鳩都軟撚埋。"},{"pid":"a3e3f0c65214b59931ac060dc5bf60a75502db93","tid":619352,"uid":21423,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T14:29:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5c20b6a7675f26408d304a1d348d85577b3578d9","tid":619352,"uid":70659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T14:30:00.000Z","msg":"唔好笑"},{"pid":"cc8fc797a274b2482edd7f99556452bd44698fbf","tid":619352,"uid":138138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T14:32:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/06/223201_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F06%2F223201_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg&h=19058c2c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b7da3c3105aa285f513ff70f84a5faf8d1f3a805","tid":619352,"uid":137997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T14:37:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"14804957111e68a7ef7da152ad89b5de02c425c6","tid":619352,"uid":139055,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T15:07:43.000Z","msg":"男人老狗學咩人着絲襪呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}